steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jit004" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit004" display
When I add new column with Name "jitcol004" Type "integer" for Table name "jit004"
When I open popup to see column infos Name "jitcol004" of table with Name "jit004"
When I update popup with textbox Name "Default value" to value "10"
When I update popup with textarea Name "Comment" to value "Column testing"
When I check checkbox popup Name "Required"
When I check checkbox popup Name "Unique"
When I check checkbox popup Name "Only integer"
